subtitleNullable: How might the rainfall Gods bless us in 2024!?
descriptionNullable:
Bangalore is getting noticeably hotter by the year. Once a haven with lush greenery and abundant rainfall, it is now turning into an overpopulated, polluted urban city. Analyze why it might be so, and which taluks are affected the most with the help of this dataset!
Contains taluk-wise annual report of rainfall received in mm.
First column of each section is expected rainfall, second section is actual rainfall.

SWM - Southwest Monsoon
NEM - Northeast Monsoon
